title: Farla Medical MediHands Nitrile Gloves, Blue Heavy Duty Disposable Gloves, Powder Free, Latex Free, and Protein Free, Medical, Food, Multi Use, Pack of 100 (M (Pack of 1000))
features: Premium Quality - Durable and puncture resistant, MediHands Nitrile Disposable Gloves offer excellent protection against cuts or abrasions.
Protein & Latex Free - MediHands non latex gloves do not contain powder latex to reduce skin irritation.
Powder Free Gloves - All MediHands gloves are powder free to avoid the risk of contamination in sensitive environments.
Ambidextrous Fitting - Latex free gloves that you can wear on either hand. Also features beaded cuff for drip protection and increased glove strength.

Medical Grade - These gloves disposable have an AQL rating of 1.5, EN455 compliant and CE approved. MediHands Gloves are produced by Farla Medical, an expert manufacturer of medical items used by practitioners worldwide.
description: Product Description About Us Farla Medical Healthcare is a Leading UK Based Supplier of High Quality Medical Equipment, Single Use Instruments, Procedure packs and Pharmaceuticals to the Primary Care Health Services. Farla is an Approved Supplier to NHS. We supply over 30,000 products and we have almost 1000 product lines through our GripSense, MediRange, Select, Madamn, MediWipes and MediHands ranges, supplying GP practices, Clinics and Hospitals throughout the UK. POWDER FREE All MediHands gloves are powder free to avoid the risk of contamination in sensitive environments. DURABLE MediHands Nitrile Disposable Gloves offer excellent protection against cuts or abrasions. AMBIDEXTROUS FITTING Each glove you find in a pack will be identical, so you can wear them on either hand. MediHands gloves are used by medical professionals worldwide. The wide range of materials and sizes available give you the choice and protection you need. Perfect for use in the beauty industry, MediHands gloves protect your hands from coming into contact with dermatistis and prevent chemical irritants from causing inflammations. Intense research and development ensure that MediHands gloves are made from durable materials, suitable for a wide variety of roles. From food safety to domestic cleaning.
